<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّى}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٦٦:</span> <span class="c3">{عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّى}</span>: قَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ: كَلَحَ وَأَعْرَضَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
